name: CoursesController
responsibilities: Map http requests regarding the Course Domain Model to respective pages

name: LoginController
responsibilities: Map http requests regarding user authentication to respective pages

name: StudentGradesController
responsibilities: Map http requests regarding the Student Grades field of the StudentRegistration DomainModel to respective pages

name: StudentRegistrationsController
responsibilities: Map http requests regarding the StudentRegistration Domain Model to respective pages

name: InstructorAuthentication
responsibilities: Grant authentication to an Instructor user

name: WebSecurityConfig
responsibilities: Defines pages that require user authentication to access

name: CourseDAO
responsibilities: Maps Course Domain Objects to the MySQL courses table row data

name: InstructorDAO
responsibilities: Maps Instructor Domain Objects to the MySQL instructors table row data

name: StudentDAO
responsibilities: Maps Student Domain Objects to the MySQL students table row data

name: StudentRegistrationDAO
responsibilities: Maps StudentRegistration Domain Objects to the MySQL student_registrations table row data

name: Course
responsibilities: Defines the data representation for the MySQL courses table row data

name: Instructor
responsibilities: Defines the data representation for the MySQL instructors table row data

name: Student
responsibilities: Defines the data representation for the MySQL students table row data

name: StudentRegistration
responsibilities: Defines the data representation for the MySQL student_registrations table row data

name: StudentRegistrationId
responsibilities: Defines the data representation for the composite primary key of the MySQL student_registrations table row data

name: CourseService
responsibilities: Defines the operations of the services that are provided by the application to the users regarding the Course Domain Model

name: CourseServiceImpl
responsibilities: Contains an implementation of the operations of the services that are provided by the application to the users regarding the Course Domain Model

name: InstructorAuthenticationService
responsibilities: Implements the operations of the services regarding authentication to an Instructor user

name: StudentRegistrationService
responsibilities: Defines the operations of the services that are provided by the application to the users regarding the StudentRegistration Domain Model

name: StudentRegistrationServiceImpl
responsibilities: Contains an implementation of the operations of the services that are provided by the application to the users regarding the StudentRegistration Domain Model

name: StudentService
responsibilities: Defines the operations of the services that are provided by the application to the users regarding the Student Domain Model

name: StudentServiceImpl
responsibilities: Contains an implementation of the operations of the services that are provided by the application to the users regarding the Student Domain Model
